## 📊 Stats & 📋 History

### 📊 Stats
- **Keyword ranking**: which keywords trigger hides most often
- **Channel ranking**: which channels get hidden most often (shows names for easy identification)
- Two-column side-by-side layout for clarity

### 📋 History
